## **7. Evaluation**

This automation was tested in real campus Wi‑Fi environments (e.g., IIT Mandi network), where connecting and logging into the captive portal repeatedly without user intervention enhances usability. System metrics show stability over hours of runtime and seamless reconnection after network drops.

